<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>Gradle on Tech In Sight</title><link>https://techinsight.pages.dev/tags/gradle/</link><description>Recent content in Gradle on Tech In Sight</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 29 Mar 2020 00:21:43 +0800</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://techinsight.pages.dev/tags/gradle/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>使用阿里云加速依赖管理</title><link>https://techinsight.pages.dev/p/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E4%BA%91%E5%8A%A0%E9%80%9F%E4%BE%9D%E8%B5%96%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86/</link><pubDate>Sun, 29 Mar 2020 00:21:43 +0800</pubDate><guid>https://techinsight.pages.dev/p/%E4%BD%BF%E7%94%A8%E9%98%BF%E9%87%8C%E4%BA%91%E5%8A%A0%E9%80%9F%E4%BE%9D%E8%B5%96%E7%AE%A1%E7%90%86/</guid><description>&lt;p>开发Java应用的过程中通常需要依赖大量的第三方包，而由于众所周知的原因，我们访问这些资源的速度非常慢，感谢阿里云给我们提供了一个选项可以快速访问这些资源。&lt;/p>
